---
layout: page.njk
title: Projects
description: Here is list of projects I have worked on from time to time.
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
renderData:
  title: Projects{% if pagination.pageNumber > 0 %} - Page {{ pagination.pageNumber + 1 }}{% endif %}
pagination:
  data: collections.projects
  size: 10
  alias: projects
  reverse: true
permalink: "/projects/{% if pagination.pageNumber > 0 %}{{ pagination.pageNumber + 1 }}/{% endif %}"
---

<section class="border-b-[3px] border-double border-b-[#f69] mb-10 pb-8">
  <p>Most of these are open-source and hosted at <a href="https://github.com/jabranr">GitHub</a> â€“ free to use and explore. You are most welcome to share your feedback, corrections and even enhancements to any of those.</p>
  <p>I also use <a href="https://gist.github.com/jabranr">GitHub Gist</a> and <a href="https://codepen.io/jabranr">CodePen</a> to share experiments from day to day work.</p>
</section>

{% for project in projects %}
  <section class="mt-4 pt-4 {% if not loop.first %}border-t-[1px] border-t-[#ddd]{% endif %}">
    <time class="text-[#666] text-sm" datetime="{{ project.date | format_date('YYYY-MM-DD') }}">{{ project.date | format_date }}</time>
    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold my-2">
      <a href="{{ project.url | url }}">{{ project.data.title }}</a>
    </h3>
    <p class="text-base mb-4">{{ project.data.excerpt | safe }}</p>
  </section>
{% endfor %}

<section class="inline-flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-base my-12">
  {% for pageEntry in pagination.pages %}
    {% if pagination.hrefs[loop.index0] == '/projects/1/' or page.url == pagination.hrefs[loop.index0] %}
      <span class="block bg-[#eee] w-8 h-8 rounded-full text-center p-1" aria-current="page">{{ loop.index }}</span>
    {% else %}
      <a class="block w-8 h-8 rounded-full text-center p-1" href="/projects/{% if loop.index != loop.first %}{{ loop.index }}/{% endif %}">{{ loop.index }}</a>
    {% endif %}
  {% endfor %}
</section>
